"|   :xmap   | :xnoremap | :xunmap | :xmapclear |   -    |  yes   |   -    |        -         |   -    |      -       |    -     |
"|   :smap   | :snoremap | :sunmap | :smapclear |   -    |   -    |  yes   |        -         |   -    |      -       |    -     |
